message.body: Happy birthday!!! I hope you have the best fay!!! :-) B-) :-$
Thanks tess!!! I'm having a good day so far. The post office line was fast!
Hey!! How was your bday?? Hope it was fun! Wanted to check and see how dirt lambs eye is looking?
It's looking wayyyy better. He is such a sensitive cat! B day was super fun. Saw new Wes Anderson movie and watched Clarissa explains it all til late!
I'm so glad you had fun! How was the new wes Anderson??
Oh you know, exactly what you expect. Fun and colorful. I liked it!
If you think you'll need artificial tears for him let me know...ella has a bunch and I can ask her to bring some to dinner tomorrow!
Julian said he ran into you guys :)
Yeah we took the subway down went to an early show and ran into him! I might take bottle for the future but the compress seems to work! When does Mary arrive??
I feel bad I can't see Hunter for massage today...I just have so much to do before mary comes!
She gets here tomorrow early afternoon :)
You guys going to dinner tonight?
I told home I'd rub him down to hold him over. To next week. It's not the same though! Yr so good!
